OL,3,CTeenage girl killed in Leeds is named
OL,4,Cas police continue to question four
OL,5,Cyouths
OL,7,FA teenage girl who died in an incident
OL,8,Fin Leeds in at the weekend has been
OL,9,Fnamed locally as 16-year-old Chloe
OL,10,FWatson.
OL,12,FChloe, from Cleckheaton in West
OL,13,FYorkshire, died after she was found
OL,14,Funconscious on a street in Leeds in
OL,15,Fthe early hours of Saturday morning.
OL,17,FThe teenager had been taken to
OL,18,Fhospital, but died shortly afterwards.
OL,19,FFour teenagers aged between 17 and 19
OL,20,Fhave since been arrested on suspicion
OL,21,Fof murder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
