CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1774951543
OL,3,CTeenage girl killed in Leeds is named
OL,4,Cas police continue to question four
OL,5,Cyouths
OL,7,FChloe was named locally by family,
OL,8,Fwith a relative setting up a Go Fund
OL,9,FMe page in her memory.
OL,11,FThe relative said: "Her mum is
OL,12,Fdistraught she has left two younger
OL,13,Fsiblings behind."
OL,15,FThey added that they "wanted to create
OL,16,Fa Go Fund Me to help give her the best
OL,17,Fsend off possible", writing that Chloe
OL,18,F"didn't deserve this".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1774951543
OL,3,CTeenage girl killed in Leeds is named
OL,4,Cas police continue to question four
OL,5,Cyouths
OL,7,F"She was so full of life such an
OL,8,Finnocent beautiful soul taken too
OL,9,Fsoon."
OL,11,FA police cordon remained up around a
OL,12,Fhouse on Kennerleigh Avenue in the
OL,13,FAusthorpe area of Leeds, where Chloe
OL,14,Fwas found, over the weekend.
OL,16,FWest Yorkshire Police have since said
OL,17,FChloe's family were being supported by
OL,18,Fspecially-trained officers.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
