PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1774951543
OL,3,CTeenage girl killed in Leeds is named
OL,4,Cas police continue to question four
OL,5,Cyouths
OL,7,FTwo 18-year-old women, a 19-year-old
OL,8,Fman and a boy aged 17 were all
OL,9,Fquestioned by detectives over the
OL,10,Fweekend after being arrested at a
OL,11,Fnearby address. They were still in
OL,12,Fcustody on Sunday, police said.
OL,14,FSenior investigating officer,
OL,15,FDetective Chief Superintendent Marc
OL,16,FBowes, said: "Following our appeal for
OL,17,Ffurther information yesterday, we have
OL,18,Fnow identified the deceased as a 16-
OL,19,Fyear-old girl from the Cleckheaton
OL,20,Farea.
OL,26,@xD@NOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1774951543
OL,3,CTeenage girl killed in Leeds is named
OL,4,Cas police continue to question four
OL,5,Cyouths
OL,7,F"Her family have been informed and we
OL,8,Fare supporting them as they try to
OL,9,Fcome to terms with what has happened.
OL,11,F"Our inquiries into the incident which
OL,12,Fled to her death are continuing, and I
OL,13,Fwould appeal again to anyone who was
OL,14,Fin the Kennerleigh Avenue area in the
OL,15,Fearly hours of yesterday morning to
OL,16,Fcome forward if they have any
OL,17,Finformation which could assist our
OL,18,Finvestigation."
OL,20,FAnyone with information is urged to
OL,21,Fcontact West Yorkshire Police.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUzD@OO]
